      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "IZZY LETTS (5) was long overdue after two placings in a row before a deserved win (16.96) last time at Murray Bridge Straight. Has a strong winning record at this journey. Has the ability and looks a key chance this line-up. ELLA'S DESTINY (2) copped a check in the run and finished out of the placings when fifth (20.74) at Angle Park over 342m in a Other. Speedy runner and should be in the action early from an inside box. Key player if finds best. FLYING HUGO (4) is a talented dog who hit the ground running off the tricky draw and was never headed, winning (19.63) at Angle Park in Grade 6 over 342m. Superior out of the boxes and will be in the firing line early. Ran the fastest time on the program in his latest win. Can continue on with his winning form. REMEMBER JAY JAY (8) cannot be underestimated.",
